by all these great minds, and in the end
none of them knows anything more

96
00:06:37,597 --> 00:06:40,434
about the big questions of life than I do.

97
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:43,397
Jesus, I read Socrates.

98
00:06:43,522 --> 00:06:47,902
This guy used to knock off little Greek
boys. What the hell's he got to teach me?

99
00:06:48,028 --> 00:06:52,450
And Nietzsche, with his
theory of eternal recurrence.

100
00:06:52,575 --> 00:06:55,913
He said that the life we live,
we're gonna live over and over again

101
00:06:56,038 --> 00:06:58,750
