102
00:06:58,875 --> 00:07:04,465
Great. That means I'll have to sit through
the "Ice Capades" again. It's not worth it.

103
00:07:04,591 --> 00:07:07,678
And Freud, another great pessimist.

104
00:07:07,803 --> 00:07:11,057
I was in analysis for years.
Nothing happened.

105
