- Was I?
- Yes, you were.

188
00:12:41,317 --> 00:12:45,865
And when I brought up the idea of having
a baby, you jumped down my throat.

189
00:12:46,032 --> 00:12:49,036
- Well, I don't think it's a very good idea.
- Why not?

190
00:12:49,203 --> 00:12:52,457
Because it's the last thing
in the world we need right now.

191
00:12:52,624 --> 00:12:54,835
Why do you say that?
Is something wrong?

192
00:12:55,002 --> 00:12:57,964
- I don't know.
- Well, tell me. Should I be worried?

193
00:12:58,339 --> 00:13:02,136
- Well, you got four children.
- I want one with you.

194
00:13:02,261 --> 00:13:06,350
Well... I think we should
wait till things settle.

195
00:13:06,475 --> 00:13:08,603
What does that mean?

196
00:13:08,728 --> 00:13:12,316
