200
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:26,125
Yeah, but I... I thought you needed that.

201
00:13:26,251 --> 00:13:28,629
When we met,
you said your life was chaos.

202
00:13:28,754 --> 00:13:32,425
I know, but there's
gotta be some give and take.

203
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:36,597
Oh, listen. I don't know
what the hell I'm talking about.

204
00:13:36,722 --> 00:13:38,934
- Are you angry with me?
- No!

205
00:13:39,059 --> 00:13:42,647
