I am in love with someone else"?

210
00:13:56,456 --> 00:13:59,418
- Are you?
- No!

211
00:13:59,544 --> 00:14:03,966
But you keep asking awful questions.
It's like you want me to say yes!

212
00:14:04,091 --> 00:14:08,722
What are you talking about?
Of course not. I'd be destroyed.

213
00:14:08,847 --> 00:14:11,684
For Christ's sake, stop torturing her.

214
00:14:11,809 --> 00:14:14,605
Tell her you want out and get it over with.

215
