You're in love with her sister.
You didn't do it on purpose.

216
00:14:18,818 --> 00:14:22,031
Be honest. It's always the best way.

217
00:14:22,156 --> 00:14:24,451
Can I help you?

218
00:14:24,576 --> 00:14:27,788
