00:42:37,931 --> 00:42:43,522
When I ran into you, you seemed
just perfectly fine. You seem fine now.

620
00:42:43,689 --> 00:42:48,612
Well, I'll tell you. One day,
about a month ago, I really hit bottom.

621
00:42:48,737 --> 00:42:53,284
Ijust felt that in a Godless universe,
I didn't want to go on living.

622
00:42:53,409 --> 00:42:58,875
Now, I happen to own this rifle, which
I loaded and pressed to my forehead,

623
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,503
and I remember thinking.;
