636
00:43:42,932 --> 00:43:48,648
And I ran to the door, I didn't know what
to say. I was embarrassed and confused.

637
00:43:48,773 --> 00:43:53,112
My mind was racing a mile a minute,
and Ijust knew one thing.

638
00:43:53,237 --> 00:43:59,703
I had to get out of that house, just
get out in the fresh air and clear my head.

639
00:43:59,829 --> 00:44:03,625
And I remember very clearly
I walked the streets.

640
00:44:03,750 --> 00:44:09,842
I didn't know what was going through my
mind. It all seemed so violent and unreal.

641
00:44:09,967 --> 00:44:13,555
And I wandered for a long time
on the Upper West Side.

642
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:19,187
It must have been hours. My feet hurt and
my head was pounding. I had to sit down.

643
00:44:19,312 --> 00:44:23,568
I went into a movie house. I didn't know
what was playing. Ijust needed a moment

644
00:44:23,693 --> 00:44:26,154
to gather my thoughts and be logical

645
00:44:26,321 --> 00:44:29,742
and put the world
back into rational perspective.

646
00:44:29,909 --> 00:44:31,953
(# playing a tune)

