00:44:38,629 --> 00:44:41,966
And I went upstairs
to the balcony and I sat down.

648
00:44:42,133 --> 00:44:47,348
The movie was a film that I'd seen
many times in my life since I was a kid,

649
00:44:47,515 --> 00:44:49,643
and I always loved it.

650
00:44:49,810 --> 00:44:52,230
And I'm watching these people
up on the screen

651
00:44:52,397 --> 00:44:55,609
and I started getting hooked on the film.

652
00:44:55,776 --> 00:45:02,284
And I started to feel.; how can you even
